        </accruals>
        <bioghist id="ref9">
            <head>Biographical Note</head>
            <p>American historian.</p>
        </bioghist>
        <scopecontent id="ref10">
            <head>Scope and Content of Collection</head>
            <p>Writings, notes, correspondence, photocopies of government documents, books, other printed matter, photographs, and videotapes, relating to Jan Karski, the resistance movement and Jewish holocaust in Poland during World War II, and Jewish refugees in the Soviet Union. In part, used as research material for the book by E. T. Wood and Stanislaw M. Jankowski, Karski (New York, 1994).</p>
        </scopecontent>
